text: "Do What U Gotta Do" is a song by American recording artist Angie Stone. It was written by Isaac Lewis, Levi Stephens, Warren Jones, and Y'anna Crawley for Stone's sixth studio album Rich Girl (2012), while production was helmed by Lewis, Stephens, and Jones. Released as the album's lead single, it reached number 13 on Billboards Adult R&B; Songs. ==Track listings== ==Charts== {| class="wikitable sortable plainrowheaders" ! align="center"|Chart (2012) ! align="center"|Peak position |- |- |- |} == References == ==External links== * Category:2012 songs Category:2012 singles Category:Angie Stone songs
